        {
            "title": "中國股市收跌0.33%，科創50升超1%！分析師：警惕業績雷風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvib4xSMzsyQIvZwgu7Dkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAAG092_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com - </strong>周五，4月24日，A股市場探底回升，三大指數午後跌幅收窄，科創50升超1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今日市場跌多升少，全市場超2000只個股上升，超3300只下跌。滬深兩市成交額2.64萬億，較上一個交易日縮量1626億。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至收市，上證綜合指數收跌0.33%，報4079.9點，深證成份指數收跌0.69%，報14940.3點，創業板指數（價格）收跌1.41%，報3667.79點，中國A50期貨指數截稿前跌0.24%，報15605點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5f2da352-8c7b-33e9-b79c-1f72d7843c81-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bsz_Q8osyVJjZJrMFFBO_w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/c6940ce2d1d377e0abdb969c7b0af91e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盤面上，鋰礦概念集體爆發，盛新鋰能、金圓股份、融捷股份、江特電機、西藏珠峰升停，天齊鋰業觸及升停。晶片產業鏈震盪拉升，綜藝股份2連板，富瀚微20cm升停，華虹公司、傑華特升超10%。化工板塊表現活躍，廣信股份、江南高纖、天禾股份、三房巷升停。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">下跌方面，油氣板塊持續走弱，廣匯能源逼近跌停，准油股份、通源石油跌超6%。商業航太概念持續調整，西部材料跌停，久之洋、中衡設計、廣聯航空、通宇通訊、上海港灣等多股跌幅靠前。算力硬件方向走弱，新易盛跌超11%，兆馳股份跌停，天孚通信跌近7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巨豐投顧郭一鳴指出，A股修復行情已步入尾聲，正式進入磨頂階段。板塊輪動加速、熱點高低切換，是磨頂階段的另一大顯著表現。當前市場面臨的潛在風險不容忽視，尤其是四月底臨近，業績雷風險需重點警惕。指數波動加大、市場分化加劇，也會進一步放大業績雷帶來的衝擊，投資者需提前做多風險防範。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>財報季，美股數字睇到眼花？</span></u></strong> <strong><u><span>Warren AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>一鍵解讀數據！現在</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"772\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dwjmQAXasI_8TrgWg1zkyw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc3Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/c0f703817c02134d10f195f16c84a19b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><span><br/></span> <br/></strong></p></blockquote></div>",
